sentences.english: The door hit me in the face and I saw stars for a moment.
sentences.chinese: 我的脸撞在门上，好一会儿我都眼冒金星。

sentences.english: When that branch fell on my head, I saw stars for several seconds.
sentences.chinese: 那树枝落在我头上时，我有好几秒钟眼冒金星。

sentences.english: A swinging door hit me and I really saw stars.
sentences.chinese: 一扇旋转门撞得我两眼冒金星。

sentences.english: Felian: Don't mention three days.I will see stars just for skipping one regular meal and I will hold the wall when farting!
sentences.chinese: 别说三天了，我一顿不吃就眼冒金星，放屁扶着墙了。

sentences.english: I hit my head so hard on the tree that I saw stars.
sentences.chinese: 我撞树撞得好狠，都眼冒金星了。

sentences.english: My mother's head hit the desk. It made her see stars.
sentences.chinese: 我妈妈的头撞在了桌子上，这使她眼冒金星。

sentences.english: She had stars in her eyes when she saw the car she had won.
sentences.chinese: 当她看到她赢得的汽车后，她眼冒金星。
